Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be the leader of one of the vicious ransomware groups known as Lockbit, exposed by the government. Dropping this information like a GTA trailer was the cherry on this news. Thanks for watching!

title: The US Government Just Doxxed The Biggest Cybercriminal...
